WEBVTT

00:04:56.650 --> 00:05:01.560
who are successful are 
very often not really happy,

00:05:01.560 --> 00:05:02.800
as they could be.

00:05:04.920 --> 00:05:09.856
So if chasing control
is not the correct way,

00:05:09.880 --> 00:05:12.376
what is the correct way?

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:19.400
One way is that if we stop trying
to control people or situations

00:05:20.160 --> 00:05:24.056
but instead try to find inner control.

00:05:24.080 --> 00:05:29.376
Inner control means keeping
our mind and emotions in check.

00:05:29.400 --> 00:05:34.336
To attain this control here is a tip:
adopt a healthy lifestyle -- eat well,